  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Mechanical Field Service Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Main Duties &amp; Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform new build installations of Svanehoj pumps and ITT supported products.</li>\n  <li>Perform service and overhaul of Svanehoj and ITT supported products including machinery like pumps, compressors etc.</li>\n  <li>Supervise yard workers assigned during the repair.</li>\n  <li>Organize the repair/mechancial tasks on board and in workshop.</li>\n  <li>Finalize detailed service report after completion of each job.</li>\n  <li>Build a good relationship with our customers on-site.</li>\n  <li>Ensure that the work is excuted according to company safety and environmental guidelines and customer procedures.</li>\n  <li>Mechancial inspection, repair and troubleshooting of entire pump range.</li>\n  <li>Carry out laser alignment measurements.</li>\n  <li>Writing of reports for carried out inspections, repair, and overhaul under extreme pressure.</li>\n  <li>Travelling activity globally if required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Mechancial Engineering or a related discipline.</li>\n  <li>Able to act responsible and execute several projects at same time.</li>\n  <li>Acting responsible and trustworthy towards customers and colleagues and the company.</li>\n  <li>Able to write detailed technical reports in English.</li>\n</ul>",
