    "description": "<p>Svanehoj Singapore is a market-leading manufacturer of specialised In-line pumps for the marine and offshore industries within the areas of engine room pumps, pump room systems, fire water pump packages, exhaust gas cleaning pumps as well as sales and after-sales services.&nbsp;We are a Singapore based company with sales office located in Poole, UK, and employs approximately 120 employees.&nbsp;Svanehoj Singapore is part of the Denmark based Svanehøj Group, which also counts the recognized brand, SVANEHØJ.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>A major part of Pumps business is based in Singapore.</p>",
